(191, 1, '2019-03-21 16:10:47', '2019-03-21 16:10:47', 'Revitalized the Duluth house with Hardie Plank \r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Reglazing the windows</h2>\r\n<p>Glazing is the name of the hardened putty that creates a weathertight seal on the exterior of the window between the wood and the glass. For the glazing process all we need is a putty knife and a handful of well-kneaded glazing compound. Using the putty knife, we created perfect putty bevels. If the window is properly maintained, the glazing compound will last for many, many years.</p>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://primepaintersatlanta.com/current/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG_6036-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-163\" />\r\n\r\n<p>We also replaced existing rotted siding, with Hardie Plank vinyl siding, caulked edges and trims, afterwich the complete house and trim was painted with Sherwin-Williams Duration that has a lifetime warranty.</p>\r\n', 'Exterior Services in Duluth', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-21 16:10:47', '2019-03-21 16:10:47', '', 154, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/uncategorized/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
