(237, 2, '2019-04-11 08:54:58', '2019-04-11 08:54:58', '<p>We gave the Houchton house an exterior painting overhaul including a complete exterior repaint, caulking, rotten wood replacement, and deck staining. This beautiful house deserved attention to detail, so we made sure to pace ourselves in order to get everything ready for a perfect finish.</p> <!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>First, we assessed the integrity of the wood in the deck, quickly finding that it had been rotted and was in need of replacement. After we’d replaced the rotted wood, we caulked any cracks or places where the outside elements could damage the home from the outside, making sure to seal every one. Then, we hand scraped the surfaces of the house that we’d be painting in order to make a clean base for the paint to absorb into. Lastly, we used Sherwin-Williams Superpaint for the amazing final result.</p>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://primepaintersatlanta.com/current/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_3352_01-1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"Exterior Painting Houchton\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-230\" />\r\n\r\n<p>Superpaint comes in handy against the elements; whether it’s storming and snowy or arid and dry, this paint applies smoothly and will resist fading, cracking, and peeling. Thanks to its advanced acrylic resin technology, this paint has  outstanding adhesion and color retention and it’s also dirt-resistant and mildew-resistant.</p>\r\n', 'Exterior Painting in Houchton', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '226-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-11 08:54:58', '2019-04-11 08:54:58', '', 226, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/uncategorized/226-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(238, 2, '2019-04-11 09:36:31', '2019-04-11 09:36:31', '<p>Lilburn is a gorgeous area and all the homes in it match its amazing scenery. We were inspired to make the inside of this house just as immaculate as the outside to make this home something its owners could be proud of.</p><!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://primepaintersatlanta.com/current/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_5197-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"Interior Painting Lilburn\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-239\" />\r\n\r\n<p>We used Sherwin-Williams ProBlock®, which is an oil based primer that seals out water and dried water stains, smoke stains, grease, ink, and related odors. The topcoat end result is a uniform finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the top coat, we Stuck with Sherwin-Williams again and used their ProClassic® interior paint. This paint is a tough and durable coating that will  enhance the look of doors, trim, cabinets and furniture. It also provides amazing adhesion,and the formula prevents it from yellowing as well as giving it  a unique wet and dry hide. The finished product of the Lilburn house makes this a successful interior painting job!</p>\r\n', 'Interior Painting in Lilburn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interior-painting-in-lilburn', '', '', '2019-04-11 09:36:31', '2019-04-11 09:36:31', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/?p=238', 0, 'post', '', 0),
