(241, 2, '2019-04-11 09:49:28', '2019-04-11 09:49:28', '<p>This Suwanee house needed a complete interior painting overhaul. Our work here consisted of painting the ceilings, walls, door trims, window trims, closet interior, and we also painted the garage floor with a special epoxy coating for an outstanding finish.</p><!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://primepaintersatlanta.com/current/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_0353-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Interior Painting Suwanee\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-242\" />\r\n\r\n<p>For this project, our team dove right in, removing furniture from each room and covering everything in plastic to ensure that the homeowner’s belongings wouldn’t be stained by the paint. For each room, we used Sherwin-Williams Superpaint Interior Latex Paint because it is both a paint and primer in one, so we didn’t take up more of the homeowner’s time painting than necessary. This paint is easy to apply and hides any stains that it paints over— it is also incredibly easy to clean if needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the garage floor, we used Sherwin-Williams Pro Industrial High Performance Epoxy. This type of coating is chemical resistant and  abrasion resistant which is ideal for a garage where there’s likely high traffic and motor oil from cars being spilled.</p>\r\n', 'Interior Painting in Suwanee', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interior-painting-in-suwanee', '', '', '2019-04-11 10:00:13', '2019-04-11 10:00:13', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/?p=241', 0, 'post', '', 0),
