(258, 2, '2019-07-27 03:18:03', '2019-07-27 03:18:03', '<p>Prime Painters understands how important good service is in a booming service industry. Our goal is to give you peace of mind throughout the process of painting your home to meet and exceed your expectations. We strive to be with you every step of the way and treat each of our clients like they’re our own family by customizing each job to fit their aesthetic goals.</p><!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>With our knowledgeable staff and exceptionally talented painters, we are able to offer our residential painting customers the highest levels of service and quality, while minimizing the impact on the livability of your space. We know that the inside of each home means the world to each and every family, so we make sure to take the proper steps in covering furniture, flooring, and prepping other things inside the house to ensure that everything is just as perfect as it was before we left it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Choosing the right color for the interior of a home is one of the most crucial steps to creating a warm, happy living environment. Our expert staff is always available to discuss color schemes and paint sheen while providing complimentary test patches.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> We guarantee our work will live up to your expectations, so if you’re looking for reliable, honest interior painters in the John’s Creek area, give us a call!</p>\r\n', 'Interior Painting in John\'s Creek', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interior-painting-in-johns-creek', '', '', '2019-08-14 17:05:28', '2019-08-14 17:05:28', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/?p=258', 0, 'post', '', 0),
