(262, 2, '2019-07-27 03:20:21', '2019-07-27 03:20:21', '<p>Prime Painters offers the most convenient and efficient professional residential painting services for both large and small projects. Whether you’re looking to paint a bedroom, kitchen, or any surface, we have experienced painters that are dedicated to making the process as simple and cost-effective for you as possible. We stand behind our products and services, and will always get the job done right the first time.</p><!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Prime Painters are experienced in cabinet painting, wood staining, carpentry, and many other services your home may need in order to bring out its hidden beauty. Our house painters will come to your house prepared to get the job done with all the necessary materials. Whatever your desired interior look, Prime Painters can deliver. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a reliable resource for painting (interior and exterior), staining, refinishing, and even repairs. We will always work with you to ensure our work falls within your budget so you can have peace of mind.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remember, when you’re looking for experienced, exceptional interior painters in Buford, give us a call and we’ll show you the difference between us and the other guys.</p>\r\n', 'Buford Interior Painting', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'buford-interior-painting', '', '', '2019-08-14 17:10:06', '2019-08-14 17:10:06', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/?p=262', 0, 'post', '', 0),
