(264, 2, '2019-07-27 03:21:03', '2019-07-27 03:21:03', '<p>Prime Painters provides a range of custom interior painting services as well as a line of other home improvement services that compliment painting projects. Whether you’re having your entire interior painted or refreshing the paint in your home’s bedrooms, our team approaches every painting project with an eye for detail.</p><!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>We know that choosing the color for any interior painting job can be difficult, but you can trust our team of experts to help you on your journey to picking the right one. We will work with you and help you decide what color scheme works best for your home before ever putting a brush to a wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you schedule your painting project with us, we’ll give you a complimentary consultation to discuss the vision you have for your home, go over color schemes, assess any damaged walls in need of repair, and anything else that needs to be done so we have a complete understanding of our project before ever starting the job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prime Painters has passionately served Alpharetta for many years, and it’s all thanks to our incredible customers! Whether your project is big or small, you can trust Prime Painters to help you bring your dream home to life.</p>\r\n', 'Interior Painting in Alpharetta', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interior-painting-in-alpharetta', '', '', '2019-08-14 17:11:39', '2019-08-14 17:11:39', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/?p=264', 0, 'post', '', 0),
