(4, 1, '2019-02-09 00:01:59', '2019-02-09 00:01:59', '<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <div class=\"hero\">\r\n        <ul class=\"menu\">\r\n            <li>\r\n                <div class=\"graphic\"><img src=\"[get_theme_dir]/img/hero/639822898.jpg\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"label\">\r\n                    interiors\r\n                </div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <div class=\"graphic\"><img src=\"[get_theme_dir]/img/hero/583735350.jpg\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"label\">\r\n\r\n                exteriors\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <div class=\"graphic\"><img src=\"[get_theme_dir]/img/hero/186223431.jpg\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"label\">\r\n\r\n                deck staining\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <div class=\"graphic\"><img src=\"[get_theme_dir]/img/hero/622008430.jpg\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"label\">\r\n\r\n                residential\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <div class=\"graphic\"><img src=\"[get_theme_dir]/img/hero/647802542.jpg\"></div>\r\n                <div class=\"label\">\r\n\r\n                commercial\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <ul class=\"service-board\">\r\n                <li class=\"slide slide-1\" id=\"start\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"cta-content-wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"content boxed\">\r\n                            <h2>A history of bringing visions to life</h2>\r\n                            Prime Painters takes pride in providing excellent and high quality service \r\n                            for the Metro Atlanta area. We provide amazing service for both your interior \r\n                            and exterior painting needs, as well as outstanding customer service. With over 15 \r\n                            years of experience, we will work with you to assess your needs and determine the best \r\n                            approach to meet your goals. \r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"cta\" href=\"mailto:emil@primepaintersatlanta.com\">contact the pros</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>Professional prep work makes all the difference!</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide slide-2\" id=\"interiors\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"cta-content-wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"content\">\r\n                            <h2>professional prep = professional results</h2>\r\n                            A fresh coat of interior paint can do wonders for your house. \r\n                            It can brighten the whole setting and create an entirely different atmosphere! \r\n                            Learn how we can help you make your dream home happen!	\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"cta\" href=\"tel:7708271115\">get in touch</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>let us bring your exterior back to life</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide slide-3\" id=\"exteriors\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"cta-content-wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"content\">\r\n                            <h2>time for the jones to keep<br> up with you</h2>\r\n                            Whether you want to put a fresh coat of paint to change the look of your house or <br> \r\n                            you’re looking to revive an ageing exterior, our expertise can help make your<br> \r\n                            home look better than new.\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"cta\" href=\"http://primepaintersatlanta.com/exterior-painting-lawrenceville/\">find out more</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>let us finish what you start.. or stain</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide slide-4\" id=\"deckstaining\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"cta-content-wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"content boxed\">\r\n                            <h2>Breathe new life into an old deck and make it look like new</h2>\r\n                            Polish up your patio and make your outdoor space \r\n                            the ideal spot to watch that football game or be the \r\n                            envy of the neighborhood by hosting the dinner party \r\n                            of the century! \r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"cta\" href=\"tel:7708271115\">get in touch</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>\r\n                        Not just a pretty face: protect and add <br> some polish at the same time! \r\n                    </h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide slide-5\" id=\"residential\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"cta-content-wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"content boxed\">\r\n                            <h2>We\'ve got you covered, as well as your house</h2>\r\n                            Paint protects your home from the elements like harmful UV rays as well as \r\n                            moisture which can cause wood to rot. Paint can also protect your home from pesky \r\n                            wood-loving insects. Not only can a fresh coat of paint protect your home, but it \r\n                            likely will bring up your home’s value, too!\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"cta\" href=\"tel:7708271115\">get in touch</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>from banks to bistros</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide slide-6\" id=\"commercial\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"cta-content-wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"content boxed\">\r\n                            <h2>prompt and professional service every time</h2>\r\n                            Prime Painters provides prompt, professional service to many kinds of \r\n                            businesses while working within your budget and time frame. We work hard \r\n                            so you won’t need to.\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"cta\" href=\"tel:7708271115\">request a quote</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"testimonials\">\r\n        <h4 class=\"header\">what our clients say</h4>\r\n        <ul class=\"testimonials-wrapper\">\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Shawn m simpson</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Prime Painters completed our house early and it looks great. I would recommend them.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Raechel Gurlie</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">My husband found Prime Painters LLC on Kudzu along with a few other companies after we had a leak in our kitchen from our master bath and decided to get them repainted. When we met Emil, we could tell he was serious about his work and\r\n                his company would do a great job. We thought his estimate was fair, and we are impressed with his work. Emil is very detailed and made sure the job was done right. We will definitely use Prime Painters again for our painting needs.\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Phil Blanton</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Emil and his team are thorough and prompt. Their attention to detail is next level. Even with the rain my job was finished with the utmost care and professionalism. By far my best experience ever with a painting company.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Henry Sullivan</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Emil and his crews did an amazing job painting our home\'s exterior from the initial pressure washing to the last walk-through. They arrived when scheduled and worked professionally throughout the project. Our home looks updated and incredible!\r\n                We have had many neighbors come to compliment the job and ask for the painters\' information. We used Prime Painters years ago in a previous home for inside painting and were just as pleased with both jobs done!\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Ben Hollonds</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">I\'m very pleased with the work done and would highly recommend Prime Painters. When it\'s time to do the exterior of my house, I know whom to call.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            \r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Jessica Sanders</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Simply put, this was a great experience. They were quick with the estimate and quick to do the work. There was a lot of rot in the wood around my house and they replaced it all. The carpentry and the paint looks great!</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Gigi Doby</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">I needed paint to cover deep orange, dark purple, hot pink, etc. Prime Painters came thru like champs in painting as many coats as needed to cover the old colors (with light blues and grays) and still keeping within the time frame originally\r\n                stated. I\'m very pleased with the work done and would highly recommend Prime Painters. When it\'s time to do the exterior of my house, I know who I\'m calling!\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Stanley and Cindy</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">The house needed an exterior painting and the ceiling was leaking while we were out. We had another company did the painting before; therefore, we could tell Prime Painters did an awesome job. They took care of the surprised leaking problem\r\n                at the same time as well. It\'s a great job done with an affordable price. We are happy with the results.\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Tim Mooney</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Emil and Crew were Professional fast and used the best quality materials. Our Interior was done to perfection.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2019-04-22 06:54:01', '2019-04-22 06:54:01', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//?page_id=4', 0, 'page', '', 0),
