d worked professionally throughout the project. Our home looks updated and incredible!\r\n                We have had many neighbors come to compliment the job and ask for the painters\' information. We used Prime Painters years ago in a previous home for inside painting and were just as pleased with both jobs done!\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Ben227</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">I\'m very pleased with the work done and would highly recommend Prime Painters. When it\'s time to do the exterior of my house, I know whom to call.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            \r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Duluth_Jessica</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Simply put, this was a great experience. They were quick with the estimate and quick to do the work. There was a lot of rot in the wood around my house and they replaced it all. The carpentry and the paint looks great!</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">GiDoby</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">I needed paint to cover deep orange, dark purple, hot pink, etc. Prime Painters came thru like champs in painting as many coats as needed to cover the old colors (with light blues and grays) and still keeping within the time frame originally\r\n                stated. I\'m very pleased with the work done and would highly recommend Prime Painters. When it\'s time to do the exterior of my house, I know who I\'m calling!\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">StanleyCindy</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">The house needed an exterior painting and the ceiling was leaking whil