 service. With over 15 \r\n                        years of experience, we will work with you to assess your needs and determine the best \r\n                        approach to meet your goals. \r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <a class=\"cta\" href=\"contact\">contact the pros</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>Professional prep work makes all the difference!</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide\" id=\"interiors\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"content\">\r\n                        <h2>professional prep = professional results</h2>\r\n                        A fresh coat of interior paint can do wonders for your house. \r\n                        It can brighten the whole setting and create an entirely different atmosphere! \r\n                        Learn how we can help you make your dream home happen!	\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <a class=\"cta\" href=\"contact\">get in touch</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>let us bring your exterior back to life</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide\" id=\"exteriors\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"content\">\r\n                        <h2>exteriors header</h2>\r\n                        Whether you want to put a fresh coat of paint to change the look of your house or you’re looking \r\n                        to revive an ageing exterior, our expertise can help make your home look better than new.\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <a class=\"cta\" href=\"contact\">find out more</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>let us finish what you start.. or stain</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide\" id=\"deckstaining\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"content\">\r\n                        <h2>Breathe new life into an old deck and make it look like new</h2>\r\n                        Polish up your patio and make your outdoor space \r\n                        the ideal spot to watch that football game or be the \r\n                        envy of the neighborhood by hosting the dinner party \r\n                        of the century! \r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <a class=\"cta\" href=\"contact\">get in touch</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>\r\n                        Not just a pretty face: protect and add some polish at the same time! \r\n                    </h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide\" id=\"residential\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"content\">\r\n                        <h2>We\'ve got you covered, as well as your house</h2>\r\n                        Paint protects your home from the elements like harmful UV rays as well as \r\n                        moisture which can cause wood to rot. Paint can also protect your home from pesky \r\n                        wood-loving insects. Not only can a fresh coat of paint protect your home, but it \r\n                        likely will bring up your home’s value, too!\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <a class=\"cta\" href=\"contact\">get in touch</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"transition\">\r\n                    <h2>from banks to bistros</h2>\r\n                </li>\r\n\r\n                <li class=\"slide\" id=\"commercial\">\r\n                    <div class=\"graphic\"></div>\r\n                    <div class=\"content\">\r\n                        <h2>prompt and professional service every time</h2>\r\n                        Prime Painters provides prompt, professional service to many kinds of \r\n                        businesses while working within your budget and time frame. We work hard \r\n                        so you won’t need to.\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <a class=\"cta\" href=\"contact\">request a quote</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"testimonials\">\r\n        <h4 class=\"header\">what our clients say</h4>\r\n        <ul class=\"testimonials-wrapper\">\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Shawn m simpson</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Prime Painters completed our house early and it looks great. I would recommend them.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">CurlieGurlie</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">My husband found Prime Painters LLC on Kudzu along with a few other companies after we had a leak in our kitchen from our master bath and decided to get them repainted. When we met Emil, we could tell he was serious about his work and\r\n                his company would do a great job. We thought his estimate was fair, and we are impressed with his work. Emil is very detailed and made sure the job was done right. We will definitely use Prime Painters again for our painting needs.\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Pbmore</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Emil and his team are thorough and prompt. Their attention to detail is next level. Even with the rain my job was finished with the utmost care and professionalism. By far my best experience ever with a painting company.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Hdsullivan</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Emil and his crews did an amazing job painting our home\'s exterior from the initial pressure washing to the last walk-through. They arrived when scheduled and worked professionally throughout the project. Our home looks updated and incredible!\r\n                We have had many neighbors come to compliment the job and ask for the painters\' information. We used Prime Painters years ago in a previous home for inside painting and were just as pleased with both jobs done!\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Ben227</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">I\'m very pleased with the work done and would highly recommend Prime Painters. When it\'s time to do the exterior of my house, I know whom to call.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n            \r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Duluth_Jessica</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Simply put, this was a great experience. They were quick with the estimate and quick to do the work. There was a lot of rot in the wood around my house and they replaced it all. The carpentry and the paint looks great!</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">GiDoby</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">I needed paint to cover deep orange, dark purple, hot pink, etc. Prime Painters came thru like champs in painting as many coats as needed to cover the old colors (with light blues and grays) and still keeping within the time frame originally\r\n                stated. I\'m very pleased with the work done and would highly recommend Prime Painters. When it\'s time to do the exterior of my house, I know who I\'m calling!\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">StanleyCindy</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">The house needed an exterior painting and the ceiling was leaking while we were out. We had another company did the painting before; therefore, we could tell Prime Painters did an awesome job. They took care of the surprised leaking problem\r\n                at the same time as well. It\'s a great job done with an affordable price. We are happy with the results.\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n            <li class=\"card\">\r\n                <p class=\"from\">Moonsrus</p>\r\n                <p class=\"content\">Emil and Crew were Professional fast and used the best quality materials. Our Interior was done to perfection.</p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"shade\"></div>\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-11 00:37:21', '2019-02-11 00:37:21', '', 4, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(43, 1, '2019-02-11 00:41:26', '2019-02-11 00:41:26', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"heading-title\">who we are<span> | a history of results</span></h2>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        Prime Painters is a Lawrenceville based painting company with over 15 years of professional experience.\r\n        We can handle all of your residential, commercial, and industrial painting needs on time and within budget.\r\n        All of our painters are in house, so you can assure that timeliness and availability is never an issue!\r\n        We only use the highest quality paints and materials to complete your painting job. Your satisfaction is our number one priority. We provide prompt and courteous service.\r\n        Prime Painters will treat your home as if it were our own: with the utmost care and respect.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <h2 class=\"heading-title\">how we are diffent<span> | the three p\'s</span></h2>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <h4>prep</h4>\r\n        The difference between a mediocre job and a magnificent job is taking the time to do it right.\r\n        For every job we do, we take the time to tape, mud, and cover your belongings. After the prep and painting\r\n        is done we move everything back and clean up. So when our work is finished, so is yours.\r\n\r\n        The result is a gorgeous polished product that will make you want to show it off.\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <h4>profesionalism</h4>\r\n        Prime Painters is a business and made up of people just like you. As such we also know what is\r\n        like to have work done by people who are less than the highest caliber. That is why we are so selective about\r\n        the type of people and caliber of talent that joins our team. We have the highest commitment to detail and respect\r\n        for our customers.\r\n\r\n        We have the same people working with us now for over 20 years. This means the same level of detail and skill on each and\r\n        every job we do. In other words, our crews have a proven history of quality over the years and that is why we are comfortable with\r\n        them and know you will be comfortable with them in your home too.\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <h4>paint</h4>\r\n        Top materials, benjamin moore, sherwin williams, super paint, top colors\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <h2 class=\"heading-title\">markets we serve<span> | residential &amp; commercial</span></h2>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        blah blah text here\r\n    </div> -->\r\n</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-11 00:41:26', '2019-02-11 00:41:26', '', 8, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(44, 1, '2019-02-11 00:46:30', '2019-02-11 00:46:30', '<div class=\"banner\" data-alt=\"Lawrenceville Interior Painting\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Lawrenceville Interior Painting — A facelift for your house</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n<p>\r\n        When you\'re looking for Lawrenceville interior painting services you only have to make one stop: Prime Painters.\r\n        Prime Painters provides a wide range of interior painting services based on your needs. Wether you have 10,000 square feet or 1200, we got you and your walls covered.\r\n        We’re dedicated to working with you to discover your plan and realize the vision you have \r\n        for your home. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <h2>Sheetrock Repair</h2>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        Whether your sheetrock is old and damaged from moisture, or has had some settling over time, \r\n        sheetrock repair is a common home repair project. In any interior painting project, it’s essential \r\n        to remedy any imperfections in your walls or ceiling to add to the seamless look of your room. You’ll \r\n        never know that crack in your wall was even there!\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <h2>Wallpaper Removal</h2>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        Wallpaper removal is a delicate process that requires the right tools and a lot of patience. \r\n        Many times, even if you use the correct tools, like steamers and special solvents, you just don’t \r\n        know how easily it’s going to come off. The job requires patience and lots of practice to ensure \r\n        that the wall isn’t left damaged after the wallpaper is removed.\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Interior Painting', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'interior-painting-lawrenceville', '', '', '2019-03-19 15:42:30', '2019-03-19 15:42:30', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//?page_id=44', 0, 'page', '', 0);
