(50, 1, '2019-02-11 00:47:41', '2019-02-11 00:47:41', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Commercial Painting - from banks to bistros</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <p>\r\n            We handle commercial painting with the same care and \r\n            respect as your home. Our painters have tons of experience\r\n            providing both interior and exterior painting services to all kinds \r\n            of businesses. We also work around your hours to provide the best possible \r\n            experience for you with minimal disruptions to your schedule. Whether it’s a \r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Retail Painting</h2>\r\n\r\nAt Prime Painters, we offer our services to the retail market as well as the residential. We’ve had projects in retirement homes, hotels, schools, office buildings, grocery stores, and many other buildings throughout the community. Our team uses world-class materials so you know your money’s working as hard for you as we are. We will find a solution for you that leaves a lasting impression on your clients and a great environment for your staff.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>What Can We Do For You</h2>\r\n\r\nWe offer cosmetic painting services for interiors, exteriors, walls, and floors to give your business the facelift it needs to keep customers flowing in. Prime Painters also provides solutions that go above and beyond the interiors and exteriors. We cover all the bases such as roofing, exterior walls, floors, steel structural components, and outdoor decks that may be damaged due to high traffic or environmental causes. Our team can apply protective coatings like epoxy to protect your high traffic areas and keep them looking like new for years to come!\r\n\r\n\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Commercial Painting', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'commercial-painting', '', '', '2019-04-22 06:44:33', '2019-04-22 06:44:33', '', 0, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//?page_id=50', 0, 'page', '', 0),
