(59, 1, '2019-02-11 01:46:18', '2019-02-11 01:46:18', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Exterior Painting all accross Lawrenceville</h1>\r\n    <p>Before we start any exterior painting job, we want to make sure we cover all the basics to make sure your home looks its best when it’s finished. We’ll move or cover any potted plants, cover decks or surrounding trees, then we’ll inspect with a fine-toothed comb to make sure there isn’t any mildew or mold. Next, we’ll fill any cracks or holes in the walls before pressure washing away any imperfections so that a fresh coat of paint will look its best.</p>\r\n    <p>When it comes to exterior painting, Prime Painters painters have years of experience painting nearly every surface imaginable!</p>\r\n    \r\n    <p>That includes:</p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Composite</li>\r\n        <li>Patios, Decks, and Railings</li>\r\n        <li>Wood</li>\r\n        <li>Aluminium</li>\r\n        <li>Vinyl</li>\r\n        <li>Stucco</li>\r\n        <li>And More!!</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n        Choosing a color for that you’ll love for your home is one of the toughest parts, but you don’t have to do it alone. \r\n        Our team would love to consult with you to choose a color you’ll love for years to come!\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>', 'Exterior Painting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-11 01:46:18', '2019-02-11 01:46:18', '', 32, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(60, 1, '2019-02-11 01:52:48', '2019-02-11 01:52:48', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Exterior Painting in Lawrenceville — Be the envy of your neighborhood</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        Before we start any exterior painting job, we want to make sure we cover \r\n        all the basics to make sure your home looks its best when it’s finished. We’ll \r\n        move or cover any potted plants, cover decks or surrounding trees, then we’ll inspect \r\n        with a fine-toothed comb to make sure there isn’t any mildew or mold. Next, we’ll fill any \r\n        cracks or holes in the walls before pressure washing away any imperfections so that a fresh coat of \r\n        paint will look its best. We use only premium quality paints like Sherwin Williams, Benjamin Moore, Behr, \r\n        and Valspar to bring your ideal colors to life.\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <p>\r\n            When it comes to exterior painting, Prime Painters’ painters have years of experience painting nearly every surface imaginable! That includes:\r\n        </p>\r\n\r\n        <ul class=\"bulleted\">\r\n            <li>Composite</li>\r\n            <li>Patios, Decks, and Railings</li>\r\n            <li>Wood</li>\r\n            <li>Aluminium</li>\r\n            <li>Vinyl</li>\r\n            <li>Stucco</li>\r\n            <li>And More..</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <p class=\"call-out\">\r\n        Choosing a color for that you’ll love for your home is one of the toughest parts, but you don’t have to do it alone. Our team would love to consult with you to choose a color you’ll love for years to come!\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <h2>Caulking</h2>\r\n        <p>\r\n            Caulking is an important part of any exterior painting job. It serves as a watertight \r\n            sealant that protects against water damage or rotting wood. It also acts as a barrier, \r\n            protecting your home from unwanted critters like insects from getting into your home. What’s more, \r\n            it can even save you energy by eliminating drafts that let out heating and air conditioning. \r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <h2>Siding Repair & Replacement</h2>\r\n        <p>\r\n            The siding of a home is one of the first things people will notice about it. \r\n            Is yours water damaged or just looks like it’s seen better days? No worries— we’ve got you covered! \r\n            We can repair or even install replacement siding.\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Exterior Painting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-11 01:52:48', '2019-02-11 01:52:48', '', 32, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2019-02-11 01:56:32', '2019-02-11 01:56:32', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Pressure Washing Lawrenceville - uncover hidden potential</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n            Pressure washing is the most important step to prepare your home for a fresh coat of paint. \r\n            It’s important to clear away any mold, dust, cobwebs, oil, or old paint so that the new paint can be properly applied. \r\n            Pressure washing is the first step in preparing your home for success from the beginning of the job and can be performed \r\n            on brick, aluminum, granite, or asphalt.\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Pressure Washing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-11 01:56:32', '2019-02-11 01:56:32', '', 46, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//46-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(62, 1, '2019-02-11 02:01:09', '2019-02-11 02:01:09', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Pressure Washing Lawrenceville - uncover hidden potential</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <p>\r\n            While Prime Painters has extensive experience in painting, we also specialize in deck staining. \r\n            Our trusted experts have experience with any wooden surface, which means you’re always in good hands. \r\n            Not only does wood staining make your curb appeal jump, but it also has many benefits. It can help prevent \r\n            against rotting, protect from harmful UV rays, prevent the wood from splitting, enhance the woodgrain, and even \r\n            increase the lifespan of your deck or wooden surfaces.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <p>\r\n            While wood staining may seem like a simple job, it’s more complicated than you’d think! Deck staining is a \r\n            process that require meticulous work and takes several steps to be done the right way. We work with premium \r\n            materials to ensure that you get top of the line results you’ll love!\r\n        </p>\r\n        <p>\r\n            Whether you’re looking to have your deck, hardwood floors, or even wood furniture stained, you can trust us \r\n            to deliver the best possible results every time!\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Deck &amp; Fence Staining', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-11 02:01:09', '2019-02-11 02:01:09', '', 48, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com//48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
