(112, 2, '2019-02-18 23:53:19', '2019-02-18 23:53:19', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Lawrenceville Pressure Washing - uncover hidden potential</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n            Pressure washing is the most important step to prepare your home for a fresh coat of paint. \r\n            It’s important to clear away any mold, dust, cobwebs, oil, or old paint so that the new paint can be properly applied. \r\n            Pressure washing is the first step in preparing your home for success from the beginning of the job and can be performed \r\n            on brick, aluminum, granite, or asphalt. By properly managing the visual appearance of your property, you can help retain its value as well as improve it. \r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Exterior Pressure Washing</h2>\r\nPressure washing can breathe new life into your old and tired surfaces by clearing away years of grime, dirt, and even damage caused by harsh UV exposure. Our team is always careful to tailor the pressure and temperature we use based on the materials we\'re working with to make sure we avoid damaging soft pavers or stone. We also take care to assess the extent of how much your surfaces might be stained and use the proper solutions to lift any dirt, grease, or oils so they can be washed away. We also only use eco-friendly cleaning products, so you\'ll never have to worry about whether your home project will be affecting the environment or not! We\'ll clear away years of buildup from siding, stucco, driveways, roofing, with the utmost care. \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Soft Washing</h2>\r\n\r\nThe secret to exterior house washing is using a low pressure cleaning method called soft washing. You can trust our team not only to use the right pressure, but also the right temperature settings and use them both at the right distance. We make sure to deliver the maximum cleaning results without any damage to your property. \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Driveway Cleaning</h2>\r\n\r\nDriveways are one of the most high traffic areas outside of your home, so of course they suffer a lot of abuse. With cars going on and off them several times a day, there is always a risk of oil or chemicals dripping from your vehicles and leaving stains. Fortunately, we’re well versed when it comes to removing all kinds of stains from your driveway which include tire marks, oil, transmission fluid, brake fluid, rust, hardwater stains, mildew, and mold. \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Roof Cleaning</h2>\r\n\r\nRoof tile can last a long time given that it’s taken care of properly. Prime Painters provides roof cleaning services that can extend the life of your roof tile while also keeping it looking its best. Our combinations of equipment and products can remove any undesirable elements from building up and making your house look dingy and unkempt.\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Pressure Washing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-18 23:53:19', '2019-02-18 23:53:19', '', 46, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/46-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 2, '2019-02-19 00:32:47', '2019-02-19 00:32:47', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n    <h1>Deck &amp; Fence Staining: Let us finish (or stain) what you start</h1>\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\n        <p>\n            While Prime Painters has extensive experience in painting, we also specialize in deck staining. \n            Our trusted experts have experience with any wooden surface, which means you’re always in good hands. \n            Not only does wood staining make your curb appeal jump, but it also has many benefits. It can help prevent \n            against rotting, protect from harmful UV rays, prevent the wood from splitting, enhance the woodgrain, and even \n            increase the lifespan of your deck or wooden surfaces.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n            While wood staining may seem like a simple job, it’s more complicated than you’d think! Deck staining is a \n            process that require meticulous work and takes several steps to be done the right way. We work with premium \n            materials to ensure that you get top of the line results you’ll love!\n        </p>\n        <p>\n            Whether you’re looking to have your deck, hardwood floors, or even wood furniture stained, you can trust us \n            to deliver the best possible results every time!\n<br>\n<br>\n\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</div>', 'Deck &amp; Fence Staining', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-02-19 00:32:47', '2019-02-19 00:32:47', '', 48, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/48-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(114, 2, '2019-02-19 00:32:53', '2019-02-19 00:32:53', '<div class=\"banner\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Deck &amp; Fence Staining: Let us finish (or stain) what you start</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"text-section\">\r\n        <p>\r\n            While Prime Painters has extensive experience in painting, we also specialize in deck staining. \r\n            Our trusted experts have experience with any wooden surface, which means you’re always in good hands. \r\n            Not only does wood staining make your curb appeal jump, but it also has many benefits. It can help prevent \r\n            against rotting, protect from harmful UV rays, prevent the wood from splitting, enhance the woodgrain, and even \r\n            increase the lifespan of your deck or wooden surfaces.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <p>\r\n            While wood staining may seem like a simple job, it’s more complicated than you’d think! Deck staining is a \r\n            process that require meticulous work and takes several steps to be done the right way. We work with premium \r\n            materials to ensure that you get top of the line results you’ll love!\r\n        </p>\r\n        <p>\r\n            Whether you’re looking to have your deck, hardwood floors, or even wood furniture stained, you can trust us \r\n            to deliver the best possible results every time!\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Fence Staining</h2>\r\nMany homeowners love the appeal of wooden fencing around their homes. Wooden fences are great for identifying property lines, boosting curb appeal, and they’re also useful for protecting your home from harsh winds. However, being outside at all times also makes them susceptible to the elements and weather-related damage like rotting, warping, and even splintering. Fence staining not only boosts the appearance of your fence, but it can also extend the life of it as well. \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFence staining can reduce the chance of rotting or warping significantly while also providing better weather protection for your fence. It can also drastically change the look of an old and tired fence as well. Whether you want your fence stained to revitalize it and keep it looking its best for years to come or simply for aesthetic reasons, we strive to keep things as simple as possible! We’ll even check your fence for any damages and recommend replacements or repairs from there. \r\n\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Deck &amp; Fence Staining', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-19 00:32:53', '2019-02-19 00:32:53', '', 48, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
