(303, 2, '2019-08-14 17:21:29', '2019-08-14 17:21:29', '<p>Painting companies can save significant money by using inferior products. Unfortunately, this allows many companies to stuff their pockets without the customers even being aware. Prime Painters knows that the only direct route to a professional job is through professional products like Sherwin Williams paint. We also know that a fantastic finish can only be achieved by an expert crew. Our team has been serving the Suwanee area for over 15 years and we’re thoroughly recognized by the community! If you have any issues with our services, we will make it right– no questions asked.</p><!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>At Prime Painters, we don’t consider ourselves in the same league as most other painting contractors. Suwanee has many companies offering painting services, but only a few of them offer the level of attention to detail and customer service provided by Prime Painters. We understand that your home is your largest, most important asset and it’s important for us to treat it like it is our own. If you’re in need of an exterior painting in Suwanee, Prime Painters would be delighted to be your painting contractor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are in the market for any type of painting, Prime Painters  would be honored to have a chance to earn your business. We are more than willing to come to your home to give you a free consultation in order to assess what you’d like done to your home.</p>\r\n', 'Suwanee Exterior Painting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '274-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-14 17:21:29', '2019-08-14 17:21:29', '', 274, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/uncategorized/274-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
