(305, 2, '2019-08-14 17:22:59', '2019-08-14 17:22:59', '<p>Throughout Lilburn there are many professional painters who focus on home exteriors. This often times includes getting your fence painted, getting your shed painted, and of course the more obvious option would be to get the exterior of your home painted.</p><!--more-->\n\n\n\n<p>There’s a lot to know about getting your home exterior painted in Lilburn. First off, the weather has a huge significance on the time in which you can paint the exterior of a house. If it’s snowing, the paint will often times take a lot longer to dry, if it even dries at all. That’s why most people don’t call professional painting companies during winter and cold seasons. Spring, Summer, and Fall are the best seasons for exterior painting because they’re all relatively dry, and it will be easier for paint to dry without any being uneven or running.</p>\n\n<p>The painting process usually starts with pressure washing your house to remove dirt, mold, and other unwanted debris from the exterior. From there we’ll apply a primer for better adhesion of paint. The last step is to begin applying coats of paint to the exterior of the house. Without the proper application of primer it’s possible that moisture will remain under the coats of paint and then bubble and crack over time.</p>\n\n<p>Lilburn can trust Prime Painters to deliver excellent service and results every time! For a free estimate, call 770-827-1115.</p>\n', 'Exterior Painting in Lilburn', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '276-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-08-14 17:22:59', '2019-08-14 17:22:59', '', 276, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/uncategorized/276-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
