(307, 2, '2019-08-14 17:25:33', '2019-08-14 17:25:33', '<p>Prime painters offers the best residential and commercial exterior painting service at affordable, competitive rates. Our team of painters understands that your house is priceless, and that its coat of paint is the only thing between it and the elements. Not only can a fresh coat of paint keep critters and the elements at bay, but it’ll also amaze your neighbors and set you apart from the crowd. It is our goal to provide you best job and customer experience, each and every time.</p><!--more-->\n\n\n\n<p>What sets Prime painters apart from the rest of the painting companies in Wimbish? To put it simply—  the quality of our work. Our painters have over 15 years of experience and use the best tools and finish available to ensure that your house is protected from the harsh elements and looks great, too. Our complete exterior painting job includes pressure washing, scraping, sanding, and caulking, window masking and shrub protection, professional-quality spray and backroll procedures, double coatings of premium paint, and best of all, a free consultation so you’ll know everything that’s happening before we even arrive!</p>\n\n<p>Our precise procedures ensure that you will get the best job possible, and at the best price. Our painters are prompt, respectful, and professional, and our work is second to none. Settle only for the best, and don\'t forget that we offer residential interior, industrial, and commercial painting services at the same level of quality you can expect from our exterior residential services.</p>\n\n<p>Wimbish can trust Prime Painters to do an amazing exterior painting job every neighbor should be jealous of!</p>\n', 'Exterior Painting in Wimbish', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '278-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-08-14 17:25:33', '2019-08-14 17:25:33', '', 278, 'http://primepaintersatlanta.com/uncategorized/278-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
